<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Welcome to Home Page</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark ds_navbar">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand ds_navbar-brand" href="/">Kiosk App</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link ds_nav-link" href="/">Dashboard</a>
                    </li>

                    <% if (loggedIn) { %>
                        <% if (userType==="Driver" ) { %>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link ds_nav-link" href="/g2-page">G2 Page</a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link ds_nav-link" href="/g-page">G Page</a>
                            </li>
                            <% } else if (userType==="Admin" ) { %>
                                <li class="nav-item">
                                    <a class="nav-link ds_nav-link" href="/appointments">Appointments</a>
                                </li>
                                <% } %>
                                    <li class="nav-item">
                                        <a class="nav-link ds_nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                                    </li>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <li class="nav-item">
                                            <a class="nav-link ds_nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                                        </li>
                                        <% } %>

                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container text-center ds_container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Diksha's Kiosk App</h1>
        <p>This IS an all-in-one kiosk solution for businesses of all sizes. Let's get started----</p>
    </div>

    <section class="ds_section section-light">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="ds_section-title">Our Services</h2>
            <div class="row">


                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="ds_service-title">Custom Kiosks</h3>
                    <p class="ds_service-desc">We provide tailored kiosk solutions that fit the unique needs of your
                        business.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="ds_service-title">Maintenance and Support</h3>
                    <p class="ds_service-desc">Our dedicated team offers ongoing support and maintenance for all kiosk
                        models.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h3 class="ds_service-title">Software Integration</h3>
                    <p class="ds_service-desc">Seamlessly integrate your software into our kiosks with our expert
                        development team.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ds_section section-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="ds_section-title">Testimonials</h2>
            <p>Here's what our clients have to say about our services.</p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <blockquote>
                        <p>"The kiosk app transformed the way we do business. A fantastic experience!"</p>
                        <footer>- John, CEO of Corp</footer>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <blockquote>
                        <p>"Excellent customer service and brilliant kiosk solutions. Highly recommend!"</p>
                        <footer>- Sarah, Owner of TechStop</footer>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <blockquote>
                        <p>"Very professional team and robust kiosk systems. Will work with them again."</p>
                        <footer>- Michael, COO of FoodMart</footer>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer ds_footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Kiosk App by Diksha Samotra</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>